ir | عامر","text":"I feel like you talk less somehow","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:22 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"And I talk too much","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:23 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You don't have to think that","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:23 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"😲","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:24 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"So, that's not the case","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:25 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s not sir","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:26 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay ma'am..noted 😌","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:27 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I mean I do talk less to people in general. Earlier I used to talk to everyone but now it takes time to open up and be comfortable..but that's not the case here","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:28 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I am scared of talking to others as I am not capable of drawing boundaries","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:30 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Here I am just myself","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:30 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Nov 26, 2023 1:32 am","kind":"msg"}]